                            <comment id="17212913" author="dongjin.lee.kr" created="Tue, 13 Oct 2020 08:04:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=mjsax&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;mjsax&quot;&gt;mjsax&lt;/a&gt; Perhaps we need a KIP discussion for this issue, like &lt;a href=&quot;https://cwiki.apache.org/confluence/display/KAFKA/KIP-676%3A+Respect+logging+hierarchy&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;KIP-676&lt;/a&gt;. Isn&apos;t it?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17213303" author="mjsax" created="Tue, 13 Oct 2020 18:33:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Not sure if we need a KIP. Our focus is on UNIX based systems (even if we try via best effort to support other OS, too) and for UNIX based systems nothing change... Personally, I would be fine without a KIP.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Curious to hear what &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=guozhang&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;guozhang&quot;&gt;guozhang&lt;/a&gt;&#160;or &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=vvcephei&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;vvcephei&quot;&gt;vvcephei&lt;/a&gt;&#160;think?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17227084" author="guozhang" created="Thu, 5 Nov 2020 23:55:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I personally would prefer not a KIP for this straight-forward fix.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17227150" author="vvcephei" created="Fri, 6 Nov 2020 03:49:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I agree; I do not think this needs a KIP. It seems clear that the intent was to use &quot;the temporary directory&quot;, and it was simply a bug/oversight to hard-code &quot;/tmp&quot; instead of using the platform-indendent &quot;java.io.tmpdir&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In fact, I&apos;ve just reclassified this as a bug.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17227164" author="mjsax" created="Fri, 6 Nov 2020 04:53:21 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks. Good to see that we are in agreement. Will review the PR soon. Thanks for the ticket and PR &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=dongjin&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;dongjin&quot;&gt;dongjin&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17244416" author="dongjin.lee.kr" created="Sat, 5 Dec 2020 06:50:10 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;ALL //&#160;Great. Let&apos;s continue the discussion on the PR!&#160;&lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/biggrin.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17276919" author="mjsax" created="Tue, 2 Feb 2021 07:58:40 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for reporting the issue and the PR!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
